{"tid":2478525,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【石頭腳】中媒不再抵制洋貨　反罵中國品牌「消費愛國心的炒鞋」「打著“愛國”的旗號謀取不義之財」","createTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:50:16.000Z","uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa9caaf3312d9df5c467b3c9aee363a8b34e5e4","tid":2478525,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"日前被中國官媒炒得沸沸揚揚的「抵制洋貨」行動似乎嘎然而止，批判對象轉為國內的「炒鞋歪風」。多間中國媒體今天（4/7）不約而同地發文痛批，網路出現「愛國炒鞋現象」，讓國產品牌球鞋的售價飆漲30多倍。<br />\n<br />\nH&amp;M、NIKE、adidas等多家運動品牌大廠，日前因新疆人權問題，拒用「新疆棉」，引發<strong><span class=\"red\">中國抵制潮，不少中國消費者紛紛轉用國貨，改買「李寧」、「安踏」等廠牌的商品，造成價格飆漲，甚至有鞋款售價飆漲33倍。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">中國官方媒體「中國新聞網」</span></strong>今日發文批評這些炒作國產品牌球鞋的賣家，利用民眾的「愛國情懷」，囤積居奇瘋狂炒作，意圖利用網友的情懷狠狠撈一筆。文中大罵這些賣家，<strong><span class=\"red\">「打著&ldquo;愛國&rdquo;的旗號謀取不義之財，擾亂市場秩序，不僅可恥，而且可恨；不僅挑戰道德的底線，也在挑釁法律的紅線」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">《楚天都市報》</span></strong>也在今天撰文批評「消費愛國心的炒鞋」風潮，說<strong><span class=\"red\">「這不是愛國貨，這是害國貨；這是對國產知名品牌的捧殺，更是對愛國情懷的玷污和傷害」</span></strong>。文中還警告此舉可能違法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">「每日經濟新聞」</span></strong>則在評論文章中，把獲利的國產品牌列為批判對象，強調<strong><span class=\"red\">「儘管品牌方並沒有參與炒鞋，但在特殊情況下，品牌方也應當有非常之策以回應輿論關切」、「近期國產服飾品牌門庭若市，此時品牌方應更珍惜消費者突如其來的&ldquo;寵愛&rdquo;，保持價格體系的合理穩定」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，從新聞評論來看，日前因拒用新疆棉而被中國媒體痛罵的瑞典服飾品牌H&amp;M、球鞋品牌Nike、Adidas等，似乎已不再被追打。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"451e307556a532d441f766e630816fa158ffd25a","tid":2478525,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210407/UCYNFSZS2ZCZDMR7QLNMV7PVJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2FUCYNFSZS2ZCZDMR7QLNMV7PVJE%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=2f221bc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2FUCYNFSZS2ZCZDMR7QLNMV7PVJE%2F&h=baaf8116\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210407/UCYNFSZS2ZCZDMR7QLNMV7PVJE/</a>"},{"pid":"2252883a47a6f8d024e50706da72131b034edfb9","tid":2478525,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Vxq8mSgr6H7pm1CxVvKF8Zk2N7g=/760x415/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OLTDF3THBZGW5HAZRCKQZ77PQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVxq8mSgr6H7pm1CxVvKF8Zk2N7g%3D%2F760x415%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOLTDF3THBZGW5HAZRCKQZ77PQU.jpg&h=43f04861&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da41b7073ddbe859d33cf1a7f8bd07eb3eb6ece2","tid":2478525,"uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/PPkK2asOJnw3KaEvZb8rDcWoce8=/760x1350/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PLPAXPQXRJERXMNMP33GRKHISU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPPkK2asOJnw3KaEvZb8rDcWoce8%3D%2F760x1350%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPLPAXPQXRJERXMNMP33GRKHISU.jpg&h=5692355e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f488eece03abaa6562218e1464f2d665dbdeb498","tid":2478525,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"燒錯Nike<br />\n買錯李寧"},{"pid":"76dd3d477f4e04b5fada27dab59ced823ef9570d","tid":2478525,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f488eece03abaa6562218e1464f2d665dbdeb498","tid":2478525,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"燒錯Nike<br />\n買錯李寧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:31:41.000Z","msg":